<p>Petal offers shades of the 3 colors from the Shakr color scheme as globally usable LESS variables: <code>@red</code>, <code>@green</code>, <code>@blue</code>. Append <code>-l1</code>, <code>-l2</code> for lighter shades, <code>-d1</code>, <code>-d2</code> for darker shades. </p>

<p>There are also some preset classes where you can quickly add text and background color properties.</p>

